SubjectAddition to Chippewas of the Thames First Nation 42, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart for the use and benefit of the CHIPPEWAS OF THE THAMES FIRST NATION as an addition to Chippewas of the Thames First Nation 42 in the Province of Ontario, land consisting of 319.106 hectares (788.52 acres), including mines and minerals.
